Name: sex cord-stromal benign neoplasm
Definition: A chronic leukemia characterized by a clonal proliferation of eosinophilic precursors resulting in persistently increased numbers of eosinophils in the blood

Name: paratesticular lipoma
Definition: A paratesticular lipoma that is located_in the spermatic cord and derives_from fat cells.

Name: dartoic leiomyoma
Definition: A reproductive organ benign neoplasm that has_material_basis_in the dartos muscle located_in the scrotum or labia majora.
